<persName>S. F. Austin</persName> Dr to <persName>J. Bryan</persName> for <persName>Furguson </persName>a/c 1820______________    34. 00</p>

<p><persName>Reuben </persName>quit work on the <date when="1820-01-17">17th of Jany</date> and began again on the <date when="1820-02-01">1 of February (frosted)</date> 11 days lost</p>

<p><persName>Damon </persName>sick with sore knee from the <date when="1820-01-25">25 Jany</date> to <date when="1820-02-15">15 February</date> 20 days lost</p>

<p><persName>Fanny </persName>quit on the <date when="1820-02-01">1 February</date></p>

<p><persName>Damond </persName>sick quit work on the <date when="1820-02-20">20th February</date> 1 Dose Medicine</p>

<p><persName>Hugh Bradley</persName> Dr</p>

